section.invest-section
  .wrapper
    .invest-section__container
      h2.invest-section__title.font-w-bold.font-s-45
        | Вы можете открыть бизнес
      .invest-section__sub-title
        .invest-section__sub-title-line
        .font-s-26 в одном из двух форматов
        .invest-section__sub-title-line
      .swiper-bullet
        .invest-section__cards.swiper-wrapper
          .invest-section__card.swiper-slide
            img.invest-section__card-tape(src="images/invest-section-card-tape-1.png" loading="lazy" width="698" height="120" alt="icon")
            .invest-section__card-title.font-w-bold.font-s-22 Без банкротства ФЛ
            .invest-section__card-body
              .font-s-16
                | Получите описание формата и 
                br
                | узнайте размер инвестиций
              form.invest-section__form(data-feedback-form)
                input(type="text" name="honeyfield" class="honeypot" style="display:none")
                input.input.input--secondary(type="text" name="city" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Введите город")
                input.input.input--secondary(type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="off" data-inputmask="'mask': '+7 (999) 999 9999'" placeholder="Ваш номер")
                button.btn(type="submit") Получить
            img.invest-section__card-doc(src="images/invest-section-card-doc-1.png" loading="lazy" width="216" height="138" alt="icon")
          .invest-section__card.swiper-slide
            img.invest-section__card-tape(src="images/invest-section-card-tape-2.png" loading="lazy" width="698" height="120" alt="icon")
            .invest-section__card-title.invest-section__card-title--secondary.font-w-bold.font-s-22.color-white C банкротством ФЛ
            .invest-section__card-body
              .font-s-16
                | Получите описание формата и 
                br
                | узнайте размер инвестиций
              form.invest-section__form(data-feedback-form)
                input(type="text" name="honeyfield" class="honeypot" style="display:none")
                input.input.input--secondary(type="text" name="city" autocomplete="off" placeholder="Введите город")
                input.input.input--secondary(type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="off" data-inputmask="'mask': '+7 (999) 999 9999'" placeholder="Ваш номер")
                button.btn(type="submit") Получить
            img.invest-section__card-doc(src="images/invest-section-card-doc-2.png" loading="lazy" width="216" height="138" alt="icon")
        .bullet-pagination
